quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  104,1,"Woe to every persistent slanderer, persistent defamer"
  104,2,Who has gathered wealth and counted it over
  104,3,He reckons that his wealth has made him eternal
  104,4,Not at all! Indeed he will definitely be flung off into the Crusher
  104,5,And what makes you realize what the Crusher is
  104,6,(It is) the Fire of Allah kindled
  104,7,Which views the heart-sights
  104,8,"Surely it is vaulted over (i.e., with no outlet) upon them"
  104,9,In pillars widely extended